    <item>
      <title>以色列准备部署新型激光防御系统以防更多火箭弹袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/israel-readies-new-laser-defense-against-more-rocket-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列预计，经过加速制造过程后，一种可以以极低的成本拦截火箭、无人机和迫击炮的新型激光系统将于明年投入使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/israel-readies-new-laser-defense-against-more-rocket-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 11:22:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克反对党领袖警告新一轮选举抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/mozambique-eelctions-opposition-leader-warns-of-renewed-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维南西奥·蒙德拉纳 (Venâncio Mondlane) 是一位激进的反对派总统候选人，他在 10 月 9 日举行的莫桑比克大选中获得亚军，他警告称，将会有更多人抗议他所说的欺诈性选举结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/mozambique-eelctions-opposition-leader-warns-of-renewed-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰盟友在朝鲜驻军问题上面临有限选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ukraine-allies-face-limited-options-as-north-korea-troops-arrive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯决定派遣朝鲜军队来增强其厌战的军队，这让乌克兰的盟友意识到，如果不进一步升级冲突，他们几乎没有其他应对措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ukraine-allies-face-limited-options-as-north-korea-troops-arrive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利中右翼反对党在地方选举中取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/chile-s-center-right-opposition-gains-ground-in-local-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利传统的中右翼政党在周末的地方选举中赢得了几个关键的席位，在选民重返投票站选举下一任总统的一年之前，他们在反对派中占据上风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/chile-s-center-right-opposition-gains-ground-in-local-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 03:45:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>养老金改革遭否决，乌拉圭大选进入决选阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/uruguay-presidential-candidates-orsi-delgado-headed-to-runoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于两位候选人均未获得获胜所需的绝对多数票，且该国养老金制度的一项备受争议的改革法案未能通过，乌拉圭总统选举将于下个月进入决选阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/uruguay-presidential-candidates-orsi-delgado-headed-to-runoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 02:42:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在纽约与马斯克的高调活动中发表言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/elon-musk-says-he-can-cut-2-trillion-from-budget-at-trump-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 在曼哈顿中心举行了一场马拉松式集会，进入竞选的最后阶段，埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 和其他盟友也加入其中，旨在影响选民对谁能解决美国困境的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/elon-musk-says-he-can-cut-2-trillion-from-budget-at-trump-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 23:51:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
